I got killed on the Indiana game.

514
00:35:41,578 --> 00:35:44,371
That was a 12-point spread.
Who do you owe?

515
00:35:45,749 --> 00:35:48,292
No shit. Hey, Sid.

516
00:35:48,460 --> 00:35:51,503
Jack Singer owes
Tommy Korman 65 grand.

517
00:35:53,632 --> 00:35:55,341
- He's heard of him.
- Oh, great.

518
00:35:55,467 --> 00:35:57,301
I'd hate to be shacked up
with a small-timer.

519
00:35:57,427 --> 00:36:00,221
