00:39:37,939 --> 00:39:41,191
- She was pretty young?
- (woman singing)

578
00:39:41,317 --> 00:39:42,693
Thirty-eight.

579
00:39:46,823 --> 00:39:48,031
What are you gonna do?

580
00:39:49,576 --> 00:39:54,037
- Do you have kids?
