586
00:40:10,388 --> 00:40:11,763
She's a knockout.

587
00:40:13,057 --> 00:40:15,642
Chris, you'll meet him this weekend.

588
00:40:15,768 --> 00:40:19,730
- Is he coming here?
- No, he'll join us in Hawaii.

589
00:40:26,362 --> 00:40:27,571
(Jack sighs)

590
00:40:28,531 --> 00:40:31,366
Twenty, twenty, twenty.

591
00:40:31,493 --> 00:40:34,745
No. Twenty doesn't feel good.
Nineteen feels good.

592
