off with someone,

704
00:48:18,584 --> 00:48:21,086
and you can't do
a goddamn thing about it!

705
00:48:22,171 --> 00:48:25,966
Some smooth talker
with his greasy hands all over her!

706
00:48:26,884 --> 00:48:30,887
